'''Windows Server 2016'''<ref>{{cite web|last1=McAllister|first1=Neil|title=Try to contain your joy: Microsoft emits Windows Server 2016 with nano-services|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/05/04/windows_server_preview_2/|website=The Register|accessdate=2015-05-05|date=2015-05-04|archive-date=2016-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019070459/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/05/04/windows_server_preview_2|dead-url=no}}</ref>（前称'''Windows Server vNext'''）是[[微软|微软]]推出的第七个[[Windows_Server|Windows Server]]系列[[操作系统|操作系统]]，它是[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]的首個服务器版本。它的第一个早期预览版本（技术预览版）连同System Center的第一个技术预览版于2014年10月1日推出<ref name="announce">{{cite web|title=Announcing availability of Windows Server Technical Preview and System Center Technical Preview|url=http://blogs.technet.com/b/server-cloud/archive/2014/10/01/announcing-availability-of-windows-server-technical-preview-and-system-center-technical-preview.aspx|website=Server & Cloud Blog|publisher=Microsoft Server and Cloud Platform Team|date=2015-03-17|accessdate=2015-04-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318231931/http://blogs.technet.com/b/server-cloud/archive/2014/10/01/announcing-availability-of-windows-server-technical-preview-and-system-center-technical-preview.aspx|archivedate=2015-03-18}}</ref>。正式版于2016年9月26日推出<ref name=rtm-date>{{cite web|last1=Chapple|first1=Erin|title=Announcing the launch of Windows Server 2016|url=https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/hybridcloud/2016/09/26/announcing-the-launch-of-windows-server-2016/|website=Hybrid Cloud|publisher=Microsoft|date=2016-09-26|accessdate=2016-09-30|archive-date=2017-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821125130/https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/hybridcloud/2016/09/26/announcing-the-launch-of-windows-server-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于同年10月12日正式发售<ref name=GA-date/>。Server 2016没有和Windows 10同时发布，对此官方解释称这是为了在正式版发布前推出更多的技术预览版以便改善系统的稳定性。

== 功能 ==
Windows Server 2016具有多种新功能，其中包括：
* {{tsl|en|Active Directory Federation Services|活动目录联合服务}}：可以配置活动目录联合服务来验证用户存储在非[[活动目录|活动目录]]的身份，例如[[X.500|X.500]]兼容的[[轻量级目录访问协议|轻量级目录访问协议]]（LDAP）目录和[[SQL|SQL]]数据库。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/hh831502.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396#BKMK_preview |title=TechNet: Active Directory Federation Services Overview – AD FS in Windows Server Technical Preview |access-date=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2016-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317054104/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/hh831502.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396#BKMK_preview }}</ref>
* [[Windows_Defender|Windows Defender]]：Windows Server反恶意软件已經安装并默认启用（无GUI），这是一个可安装的Windows功能。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765478.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: Windows Server Antimalware Overview for Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: February 19, 2015) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409174852/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765478.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* [[Remote_Desktop_Services|Remote Desktop Services]]：支持[[OpenGL|OpenGL]] 4.4和[[OpenCL|OpenCL]] 1.1，性能和稳定性改进；MultiPoint Services角色（见[[Windows_MultiPoint_Server|Windows MultiPoint Server]]）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765476.aspx |title=TechNet: What's New in Remote Desktop Services in the Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409163303/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765476.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* {{tsl|en|Storage Services}}：中心化存储QoS策略；{{tsl|en|Storage Replica|存储副本}}（使用[[伺服器訊息區塊|SMB3]]在服务器间提供存储无关、块级别、基于卷、同步和异步复制的[[灾难恢复|灾难恢复]]）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765475.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: What's New in Storage Services in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409185056/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765475.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>存储副本复制块而非文件；文件可以正在使用。它不是多主，不是一对多和不可传递。它定期复制快照，并可更改复制方向。
* {{tsl|en|High-availability cluster|故障转移群集}}：群集操作系统滚动升级、存储副本<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765474.aspx |title=TechNet: What's New in Failover Clustering in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409181707/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765474.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* {{tsl|en|Web Application Proxy|Web应用代理}}：为[[HTTP基本认证|HTTP基本认证]]应用程序提供预身份验证，通配符发布应用程序，HTTP到HTTPS重定向，客户端IP地址传播到后端应用程序<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765473.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: What's New in Web Application Proxy in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409163432/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765473.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* [[網際網路資訊服務|IIS 10]]：支持[[HTTP/2|HTTP/2]]
* Windows Server Containers
* [[Windows_PowerShell|Windows PowerShell 5.0]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/library/hh857339.aspx#BKMK_new50 |title=TechNet: What's New in Windows PowerShell (Updated: September 30, 2014) |access-date=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414115759/https://technet.microsoft.com/library/hh857339.aspx#BKMK_new50 }}</ref>
* {{tsl|en|Soft Restart|软重启}}，一项Windows特性，跳过硬件初始化并只重置软件以加快启动流程。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.systemcentercentral.com/windows-server-technical-preview-newremoved-windows-server-roles-features/ |title=System Center Central: Windows Server Technical Preview – New/Removed Windows Server Roles and Features |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415183855/http://www.systemcentercentral.com/windows-server-technical-preview-newremoved-windows-server-roles-features/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===网络功能===
* [[动态主机设置协议|动态主机设置协议]]：因为[[網路存取保護技術|網路存取保護技術]]在Windows Server 2012 R2中已弃用，在Windows Server 2016中DHCP角色不再支持NAP<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765482.aspx |title=TechNet: What's New in DHCP in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409172132/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765482.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* [[域名系统|DNS]]：
** DNS客户端：服务绑定——增强对具有[[內送流量備援容錯機制|多个网络接口]]的计算机的支持。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765479.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: What's New in DNS Client in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409153230/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765479.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
** {{tsl|en|Microsoft DNS||DNS服务器}}：DNS策略，新的DDS记录类型（TLSA、SPF和位置记录），新的PowerShell cmdlets和参数<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765484.aspx |title=TechNet: What's New in DNS Server in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409171244/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765484.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* {{tsl|en|Windows Server Gateway}}现在支持[[通用路由封装|通用路由封装]]（GRE）隧道<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765485.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: GRE Tunneling in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: October 1, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409185847/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765485.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* {{tsl|en|IP address management|IP地址管理}}（IPAM）：支持/31、/32和/128子网；基于文件的发现，加入域的DNS服务器；新的DNS功能；更好的DNS、DHCP和IP地址（DDI）集成管理<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765487.aspx |title=TechNet: What's New in IPAM in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: February 6, 2015) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409170930/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765487.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* [[网络控制器|网络控制器]]，一个新的服务器角色来配置、管理、监控和故障排除数据中心中虚拟和物理的网络设备与服务。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn859239.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: Network Controller (Updated: December 18, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409170933/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn859239.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* [[Hyper-V|Hyper-V]]{{tsl|en|Network virtualization|网络虚拟化}}：可编程Hyper-V切换（微软[[軟體定義網路|軟體定義網路]]解决方案的新构建块）；[[虛擬局域網擴展|VXLAN]]封装支持。微软软件负载平衡器互操作性；更好的兼容IEEE以太网标准。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn931986.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |title=TechNet: What's New in Hyper-V Network Virtualization in Windows Server Technical Preview (Updated: March 11, 2015) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409182137/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn931986.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== Hyper-V ===
* 滚动[[Hyper-V|Hyper-V]]群集更新：不同于群集从Windows 2008 R2升级到2012级别，Windows Server Technical Preview的群集节点可以添加到一个运行有Windows Server 2012 R2节点的Hyper-V群集。该群集仍可继续使用Windows Server 2012 R2功能级别，直到群集内的所有节点都已經升级，群集的功能级别才会升级。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765471.aspx#BKMK_hot |title=TechNet: What's New in Hyper-V in Technical Preview (Updated: November 12, 2014) |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409155915/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765471.aspx#BKMK_hot |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 存储系统服务质量（QoS），集中、端到端监控存储性能和为Hyper-V和Scale-Out文件服务器创建策略
* 新的、更有效率的二进制虚拟机配置格式（.VMCX扩展名用于虚拟机配置数据，.VMRS扩展名用于运行时状态数据）
* 生产环境检查点
* Hyper-V管理器：备用凭据支持，低级别管理，[[WS-Management|WS-Management]]协议
* 为通过[[Windows_Update|Windows Update]]分发的Windows客户机集成服务
* 热添加和移除网络适配器（面向第二代虚拟机）和内存（面向第一代和第二代虚拟机）
* Windows/Linux{{tsl|en|secure boot|安全启动}}
* {{tsl|en|Connected Standby|备用连接}}兼容
* [[Hyper-V|Hyper-V]]的弹性存储功能将检测VM存储的连接丢失而出现的暂时删除。VM将被暂停直至连接重新建立。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://social.technet.microsoft.com/wiki/contents/articles/33635.hyper-v-aspects-in-windows-server-2016.aspx |title=TechNet Wiki: Hyper-V Features in Windows Server 2016 |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2016-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312141424/http://social.technet.microsoft.com/wiki/contents/articles/33635.hyper-v-aspects-in-windows-server-2016.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== Nano Server ===
微软宣布了新的安装选项：Nano Server。这是Windows Server的最小足迹安装选项。它不包括图形用户界面、[[WoW64|WoW64]]（用于支持32位软件）和[[Windows_Installer|Windows Installer]]，不支持控制台登录和本地或[[远程桌面连接|远程桌面连接]]的登录。所有管理均通过[[Windows_Management_Instrumentation|Windows Management Instrumentation]]（WMI）和PowerShell远程执行。微软工程师Jeffrey Snover称，Nano Server降低93%[[VHD|VHD]]大小，92%关键安全通告，并比Windows Server减少80%重新启动。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.technet.com/b/windowsserver/archive/2015/04/08/microsoft-announces-nano-server-for-modern-apps-and-cloud.aspx |title=Windows Server Blog: Microsoft Announces Nano Server for Modern Apps and Cloud |access-date=2016-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414235721/http://blogs.technet.com/b/windowsserver/archive/2015/04/08/microsoft-announces-nano-server-for-modern-apps-and-cloud.aspx |archive-date=2015-04-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.technet.com/b/server-cloud/archive/2015/04/08/microsoft-announces-new-container-technologies-for-the-next-generation-cloud.aspx |title=Server & Cloud Blog: Microsoft Announces New Container Technologies for the Next Generation Cloud |accessdate=2016-07-06 |archive-date=2015-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411000254/http://blogs.technet.com/b/server-cloud/archive/2015/04/08/microsoft-announces-new-container-technologies-for-the-next-generation-cloud.aspx |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

